transcripts.text: Reverend Raphael Warnock grew up in the projects of Savannah and made it to Morehouse on faith, grants, and student loans.  Warnock leads from Dr.  King's pulpit as senior pastor of Ebenezer Baptist Church.  Warnock knows that good deeds don't stop at the church door.  Warnock has helped register hundreds of thousands of voters in Georgia.  Warnock marches on the front lines for justice, fighting for health care, criminal justice reform, and voting rights.  Vote Raphael Warnock for Senate.  Thank you.
